NAME

    Device::LSM303DLHC - I2C interface to LSM303DLHC 3 axis
    magnetometer(compass) and accelerometer using Device::SMBus

VERSION

    version 0.014

ATTRIBUTES

 I2CBusDevicePath

    this is the device file path for your I2CBus that the LSM303DLHC is
    connected on e.g. /dev/i2c-1 This must be provided during object
    creation.

 Magnetometer

        $self->Magnetometer->enable();
        $self->Magnetometer->getReading();

    This is a object of Device::Magnetometer::LSM303DLHC

 Accelerometer

        $self->Accelerometer->enable();
        $self->Accelerometer->getReading();

    This is a object of Device::Accelerometer::LSM303DLHC

